      "side": 1,
      "message": "The versionRegex is used to determine whether a given version is a valid roll candidate and to decide whether one version is newer than another.  shortRevRegex is only used to extract a shorter string to use in the commit message.  For example in https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/2095656, the version is shortened from:\n\nchromeos-chrome-amd64-airmont-81-4044.31-1583747900-benchmark-81.0.4044.58-r1-redacted.afdo.xz\n\nto:\n\n81-4044.31-1583747900-benchmark-81.0.4044.58-r1",
